title: 820-2915 beeping 3 times
message:
3 beeps.

PP1V5_S3 - 1.5V
PP3V3_S0 - 3.33V

no liquide damage. Any idea?

title: 820-2915 beeping 3 times
message: Check RAM slot data lines with RAM slot tester. Probably a hopeless case of cracked trace under the RAM slot or CPU.
